  <span id="freeText3045719924318718056" style="display:none">"Pegboard"<br /><br />It has been carefully painted<br />with the outlines of tools<br />to show us which belongs where,<br />auger and drawknife,<br />claw hammer and crosscut saw,<br />like the outlines of hands on the walls<br />of ancient caves in France,<br />painted with soot mixed with spit<br />ten thousand years ago<br />in the faltering firelight of time,<br />hands borrowed to work on the world<br />and never returned.<br /></span>
