              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2263585773550722504">This was just fantastic. I read a lot of poetry and I rate my favorites. Kooser is 1A and Billy Collins is 1B. Kooser poems are like word snapshots that capture a moment of life and remind you of the intensity, depth, and value of beling alive. This is a must read book for poets and even people who think they hate poetry will like this book.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


